<h5>Fonts</h5>
<p>You can include this kind of examples using the @font-example filter followed by properties for the fonts:</p>
<pre><code>@font-example 12px Arial
</code></pre>
<p>
  This way, the font example will be appear, with the font family and the given size, a series of characters 
  from A to Z(a-z),  digits from 0 to 9 and some special characters.<br>
  Also, you can include a specific text with the selected font adding it below:
</p>
<pre><code>@font-example 12px Arial
My example
</code></pre>
